          "description": "Dr Catherine Lee has been my general practitioner doctor at the Canal Street facility for over 20 years (since the 9/11  tragedy).\n\nI've received outstanding care from Dr. Lee as well as  other physicians and staff at the Charles Wang Center.\n\nThe facilities and staff's care, attention to detail and ability to provide excellent health care (which has kept me in good health, outliving most of the males in my family, makes the Charles Wang healthcare facility the health care model that other facilities should take inspiration from.\n\nMy doctor actually reads my blood tests or outside exams that I take and calls me within hours of any noted concerns).\n\nI can't think more highly of or say enough good things about this facility. Even when I had moved out of state for a while, I would have to fly back to NYC because there is a lot of bad health care out there and no where was my health as much as a concern here.",
