          "description": "I had a very disappointing experience with Dr. Lily Wong. I came in feeling vulnerable and concerned because I previously had an ectopic pregnancy, and I wanted to make sure this pregnancy was progressing safely. Instead of receiving compassion and reassurance, Dr. Wong was cold, dismissive, and rude throughout the appointment.\n\nRather than helping ease my anxiety, she made me feel even more insecure and stressed. During such a sensitive and emotional time, I expected empathy and proper bedside manner, but unfortunately that was not my experience. My concerns did not feel heard or taken seriously.\n\nPatients deserve kindness, respect, and support, especially during pregnancy. Sadly, this visit left me feeling worse than when I arrived. I would not return to this doctor or recommend this office to others seeking caring medical attention.",
